Rupee Depreciation in ‘So Short a Time’ a Concern, Gokarn Says

-- B y   S h a m i m   A d a m
-- 
2011-09-25T14:32:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/rupee-depreciation-in-so-short-a-time-a-concern-gokarn-says.html
The decline in the Indian rupee in
“so short a time” is a concern and is a result of global
financial-market conditions, Reserve Bank of India Deputy
Governor Subir Gokarn said in a speech in  Washington  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
